OL,3,CAverage price of GP appointment in
OL,4,CGuernsey rises above #70
OL,6,FThe average price of a ten-minute
OL,7,Fappointment with a GP in Guernsey has
OL,8,Fincreased to #70.50.
OL,10,FSome medical professionals now fear
OL,11,Fthat this latest rise will mean
OL,12,Fislanders won't seek healthcare when
OL,13,Fthey are unwell, which could cost the
OL,14,Ftaxpayer more money in the long run.
OL,16,FIt's a specific concern for the
OL,17,FGuernsey group CareWatch which
OL,18,Fbelieves rising prices for GP
OL,19,Fappointments will put people off from
OL,20,Fseeing a doctor, leading to strain on
OL,21,Fother services.
