OL,3,CAverage price of GP appointment in
OL,4,CGuernsey rises above #70
OL,6,FThe group's chair, Bella Farrell, has
OL,7,Fbeen speaking to ITV News. She said:
OL,8,F"What we will be concerned about is
OL,9,Fthat vulnerable people can access
OL,10,Fprimary care because we know the
OL,11,Fimplications of them not being able to
OL,12,Faccess primary care early.
OL,14,F"This is an implication for everybody
OL,15,Fwhen secondary care costs more."
OL,17,FAcross Guernsey's three providers of
OL,18,FGP surgeries, pay-on-the-day
OL,19,Fappointments, generally lasting 10
OL,20,Fminutes or less, range from #69 to #72.
