OL,6,FAn extended appointment lasting at
OL,7,Fleast 20 minutes, ranges from #161.50
OL,8,Fto #166.
OL,10,FThose under 18-years-old will be
OL,11,Fcharged either #25 or #15 for an
OL,12,Fappointment.
OL,14,FThe State of Guernsey pays a #12
OL,15,Fcontribution towards the cost of a
OL,16,Fprimary care GP appointment.
