OL,3,CAverage price of GP appointment in
OL,4,CGuernsey rises above #70
OL,6,FThere are many reasons why GP prices
OL,7,Fincrease and some of them include:
OL,8,Finflation, the increasing cost of
OL,9,Fmedical supplies and insurance as well
OL,10,Fas wages for employees working in GP
OL,11,Fpractices.
OL,13,FOne island politician has already
OL,14,Fasked Health and Social Care to allow
OL,15,Fpharmacists to deliver repeat
OL,16,Fprescriptions rather than the need for
OL,17,Fa GP appointment.
