OL,3,CAverage price of GP appointment in
OL,4,CGuernsey rises above #70
OL,6,FGuernsey resident Emily has complex
OL,7,Fmedical needs and can no longer get
OL,8,Fhealth insurance. She receives help
OL,9,Ffrom income support but is worried
OL,10,Fabout the new cost of a GP appointment.
OL,12,FShe says: "In the scheme of things it
OL,13,Fis a lot of money.
OL,15,F"I understand and respect that GPs are
OL,16,Ftrained and qualified, which takes a
OL,17,Flot of work behind the scenes. I see
OL,18,Fit from two sides. But actually, when
OL,19,Fyou go and see a GP you can't do a
OL,20,Fpayment plan, you've got to pay for it
OL,21,Fthere and then.
